description: This file defines a server-side function 'generateStaticParams' used for static site generation, specifically to handle dynamic route parameters ('rideId') in a bike taxi booking system. It exports an empty array to indicate no static ride IDs are known at build time, enabling client-side hydration.

methods.name: export function generateStaticParams(): Array<{ rideId: string }> { generateStaticParams
methods.description: Generates static parameters for the ride route, returning an empty array indicating no static ride IDs are pre-known at build time.
